The '''Mimics and Gesture Theatre''' is a theatre located in the [[Eastern Administrative Okrug]] of [[Moscow]], [[Russia]].<ref>[http://government.moscow.ru/en/capital_russia/territorial_authorities/vao/ Moscow International Portal] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902065601/http://government.moscow.ru/en/capital_russia/territorial_authorities/vao/ |date=2009-09-02 }} by Department of Foreign Economic and International Relations of the City of Moscow</ref> It offers special sessions for [[deaf]] people.

The theatre is located in Izmailovsky bulv., 39/41 ([[Pervomayskaya (Moscow Metro)|Pervomayskaya]] metro station)<ref>[http://expat.ru/places.php?sect=5 Places/Theatres] en Expat.ru</ref>

